
Overview of verb stiffen

The verb stiffen has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (11) stiffen -- (become stiff or stiffer; "He stiffened when he saw his boss enter the room")
2. (2) stiffen -- (make stiff or stiffer; "Stiffen the cream by adding gelatine")
3. stiffen, tighten, tighten up, constrain -- (restrict; "Tighten the rules"; "stiffen the regulations")
